Apple’s Siri IPhone Software Struggles With Accents, FT Reports

-- B y   K a r i   L u n d g r e n
-- 
2011-10-15T07:50:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-15/apple-s-siri-iphone-software-struggles-with-accents-ft-reports.html
Apple Inc. (AAPL) ’s latest 4S iPhone has
difficulty recognizing accents, frustrating users outside of the
U.S., the Financial Times reported.  Customers also had difficulty upgrading software, the
newspaper said, without indicating where it got the information.
The phone struggles with non-U.S. accents and local business
information outside the U.S. is limited, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
